Partner Relationship Associate
Ebury Bank - So Paulo - Office based



We are looking for an Partner Relationship Associate professional who is multi-tasking and organized, who enjoys interacting with partners and clients, seeking to help us manage operations and registrations with internal areas.
What you'll do as a Partner Relationship Associate:

Frequent interface with sales and execution teams, focusing on supporting foreign exchange operations;
Continuous monitoring of documentation flow (registration and foreign exchange), aiming for a high standard in client experience;
Focus on increasing speed and quality of internal processes;
Interaction with other areas of the Bank to bridge internal requests with clients.

What you'll need:

Advanced knowledge of Word, Excel, and PowerPoint;
Prior experience in foreign exchange or foreign trade;
Advanced/Fluent English and Portuguese

